verbose_text: On the other hand, another study by a different group found that recombinant HA proteins from an H5N1 and a 2009 H1N1 virus were able to induce DC activation of murine DCs in a MyD88 / TLR4 dependent manner, indicating a possible role for this Toll like receptor (TLR) in recognition of IAV HA.
